quran[27{c,v,t}:
55,41,gunehgaar apne chehray hi se pehchan liye jayen ge to peshani ke balon aur paon se pakar liye jayen ge
55,42,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,43,yahi woh jahannum hai jisay gunehgaar log jutlatay they
55,44,woh dozakh aur kholtey hue garam pani ke darmain ghumte phrin ge
55,45,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,46,aur jo shakhs apne perwar-digaar ke samnay kharray honay se dara is ke liye do baagh hain
55,47,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,48,un dono mein bohat si shaakhen ( yani qisam qisam ke khushkabriyan ke darakht hain )
55,49,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,50,un mein do chashmay beh rahay hain
55,51,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,52,un mein sab meway do do qisam ke hain
55,53,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,54,( ahal jannat ) aisay bichonon par jin ke astar atlas ke hain takiya lagaye hue hon ge. aur dono baghoon ke meway qareeb ( jhuk rahay ) hain
55,55,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,56,un mein neechi nigah wali aurtain hain jin ko ahal jannat se pehlay nah kisi ensaan ne haath lagaya aur nah kisi jin ne
55,57,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,58,goya woh Yaqoot aur Marjaan hain
55,59,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,60,neki ka badla neki ke siwa kuch nahi hai
55,61,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,62,aur un baghoon ke ilawa do baagh aur hain
55,63,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,64,dono khoob gehray sabz
55,65,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,66,un mein do chashmay ubal rahay hain
55,67,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
